-- [[ 显示每个人手牌数的小方块 --]]
para_disp = {
    click_function = "empty_func",
    function_owner = self,
    label          = "0",
    position       = {0, 1, 0},
    rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
    width          = 1500,
    height         = 1000,
    font_size      = 2000,
    color          = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5},
    font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
}

--[[ The onLoad event is called after the game save finishes loading. --]]
function onLoad()
    params = {
        click_function = "get_card",
        function_owner = self,
        label          = "初始发牌",
        position       = {0, 1, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 3400,
        height         = 1000,
        font_size      = 800,
        color          = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5},
        font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
        tooltip        = "点击按钮为每位玩家发五张牌",
    }
    sq = getObjectFromGUID('267d39')
    sq.createButton(params)

    disp1 = getObjectFromGUID('93c8fd')
    disp1.createButton(para_disp)
    disp2 = getObjectFromGUID('d55bcc')
    disp2.createButton(para_disp)
    disp3 = getObjectFromGUID('6ee1f8')
    disp3.createButton(para_disp)
    disp4 = getObjectFromGUID('fe0a7b')
    disp4.createButton(para_disp)

    -- print('NBNBNB')
end

-- [[ 发牌 --]]
function get_card(obj, color, alt_click)
    if alt_click then
        return
    end
    local deck = getObjectFromGUID('6049c7')
    local cards = deck.getObjects()
    local players = getSeatedPlayers()
    for i, player in ipairs(players) do
        for j = 1, 5 do
            local card = cards[1]
            deck.takeObject({
                position = {0, 0, 0},
                rotation = {0, 180, 0},
                smooth   = false,
                index    = 0,
                callback_function = function(obj)
                    obj.deal(1, player)
                end
            })
        end
    end
end

function get_disp_id(color)
    if color == 'White' then
        return '93c8fd'
    elseif color == 'Purple' then
        return 'd55bcc'
    elseif color == 'Green' then
        return '6ee1f8'
    elseif color == 'Orange' then
        return 'fe0a7b'
    end
end

--[[ 实时显示每位玩家的手牌数 --]]
function show_hand()
    local players = Player.getPlayers()
    local playerid = getSeatedPlayers()
    for i, player in ipairs(players) do
        -- print(i)
        -- print(player)
        local pid = playerid[i]
        -- print(pid)
        local hand = player.getHandObjects()
        local hand_num = #hand
        -- print(hand_num)
        local disp_id = get_disp_id(pid)
        -- print(disp_id)
        local hand_num_obj = getObjectFromGUID(disp_id)
        hand_num_obj.editButton({
            label = hand_num,
        })
    end
end

--[[ The onUpdate event is called once per frame. --]]
function onUpdate()
    --[[ print('onUpdate loop!') --]]
    show_hand()
end

function empty_func()
end
